### Teams Endpoints - FIFPRO2K26 UEFA Champions League

# Get All Teams
GET http://localhost:3000/api/teams

###

# Get Team by ID (usa un ID real de la base de datos)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/teams/TEAM_ID_AQUI

###

# Create Team
POST http://localhost:3000/api/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Inter Milan",
  "shortName": "INT",
  "country": "Italia",
  "colors": {
    "primary": "#0068A8",
    "secondary": "#000000"
  },
  "logoUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/05/FC_Internazionale_Milano_2021.svg"
}

###

# Update Team
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/teams/TEAM_ID_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "FC Internazionale Milano",
  "shortName": "INTER"
}

###

# Delete Team
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/teams/TEAM_ID_AQUI

###

# Delete Team
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/teams/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
